"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"909a46ef5256ba9699ad5e943425c9bed1f88559","tid":2217543,"uid":63863,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"187dc262f8b1527b1a9ca26f095457833bc60ba5","tid":2217543,"uid":295934,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c0f13d17129b50118fa7b81fd05bf333306724ea","tid":2217543,"uid":284630,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"a9337681f25bef8cfa5030c5d3066fa9bea8b7f2","tid":2217543,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T14:12:41.000Z","msg":"點睇呢隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=balapZJ-oIs&amp;ab_channel=HackenLeeVEVO\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DbalapZJ-oIs%26ab_channel%3DHackenLeeVEVO&d=awVbgeYyyy76%2F43Y8QfwzrQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=4c7d9e6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=balapZJ-oIs&amp;ab_channel=HackenLeeVEVO</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T14:38:31.000Z","msg":"唱得幾好, 但聽左幾十秒就熄左<br />\n佢唱所有歌都好似唱緊同一隻歌咁, 冇乜變化<br />\n不過呢隻歌張國榮唱得太好<br />\n即使係張學友唱過風繼續吹, 都冇乜特別<br />\n反而藍校長求其咁唱仲有少少睇頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唱歌真係好講天份<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LvLGuT8eyOg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DLvLGuT8eyOg&d=awVbgeYyyy76%2F43Y8QfwzrQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=4c36671b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LvLGuT8eyOg</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T22:51:43.000Z","msg":"巴打講得太好，雖然好憎藍校長，不過人地唱得有感染力<br />\n宋生唱得非常好，有99分，但就係差左最關鍵嘅感染力<br />\n佢所有歌都係，你唔會想聽得耐<br />\n同埋就算比佢唱唔同style嘅歌，佢都係用幾乎同一種方式去演繹，啲歌唔耐聽<br />\n利申：細個曾經有排好鍾意聽宋禮勤"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T01:30:20.000Z","msg":"打多個比喻，李克勤唱浮誇尾段最高音，我信佢可以完美咁唱到出黎，但係感染力唔會夠eason尾尾有少少崩潰既感覺。相反，李克勤個感染力係去啲好力量，需要好完美去表現既歌。<br />\n<br />\n所以幾時都話佢揀錯歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />演奏廳個排未幾好。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢玩呢類再tune少少，唔同風格應該再紅啲。係唔知點解早十年，全世界都興同一個風格。"},{"pid":"1ea4d4d7c38f48d8f5684b03be3c31c7677e5f6d","tid":2217543,"uid":193476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T01:44:15.000Z","msg":"唱歌好難聽"},{"pid":"c6638e682681ac6963c48294a7937eed9bc3c1f1","tid":2217543,"uid":85461,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T01:44:56.000Z","msg":"李克用呀李克勤"},{"pid":"78d7da8c4ea0258364a3eb659d927a7a3d9d1573","tid":2217543,"uid":190771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T01:48:35.000Z","msg":"咩唔紅 紅 紅到發黑"},{"pid":"5705eee54c929847de7cf11b40a546fc1dd0c80a","tid":2217543,"uid":4282,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T01:50:48.000Z","msg":"李克勤把聲現場聽有加乘 舒服到癲...<br />\n錄音已經表現唔到果鍾味道 咪會覺得悶"},{"pid":"57770f3d001929b22baf95365f3d6b175b3a7f93","tid":2217543,"uid":246787,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0687695a36a479b20818b84b498dbceca7d672c6","tid":2217543,"uid":63670,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T23:11:23.000Z","msg":"真心一般般<br />\n張敬軒屌打佢啦<br />\n<br />\n寧願聽吳浩康<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T04:24:40.000Z","msg":"軒仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nDeep就不了 聽佢不如聽eason 而且佢啲吸毒喪溝女醜聞我的確唔多鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"345be08b7ebf335bb4a4bef9041aa9d6e73585d9","tid":2217543,"uid":29499,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T04:41:37.000Z","msg":"80、90、00、10、20年代都仲活躍仲有冠軍歌，好似得宋生一個<br />\n都係成就嚟嘅，點會唔算紅呢<br />\n不過做唔到最紅嗰幾個啫"},{"pid":"0e970147fb922d0eb42d3434798e487bd2cf